ygData.messageBody:
The regular giant skeletons in Rathe Mountains were blue to yellow to
me at 24th. I think the darkbone skel is even higher still. Someone
killed it for me, and I looted it. I haven't ran to Mistmoore yet,
though.
From what I understand, that darkbone skel is high 20s.
